WEBVTT

00:10:29.720 --> 00:10:35.216
koliko jih je dom civilizaciji, ki si je
sposobna kot mi izmisliti

00:10:35.240 --> 00:10:37.440
projekte, kot je Breakthrough Starshot?

00:10:38.480 --> 00:10:39.736
Bivalnost -

00:10:39.760 --> 00:10:42.576
prava vrsta planeta
okoli prave vrste zvezde -

00:10:42.600 --> 00:10:44.936
in bilijon postane milijarda.

00:10:44.960 --> 00:10:46.296
Stabilnost -

00:10:46.320 --> 00:10:49.736
podnebje, ki ostane neškodljivo eone let -

00:10:49.760 --> 00:10:51.616
in milijarda postane milijon.

00:10:51.640 --> 00:10:52.840
Življenje se mora začeti -

00:10:53.600 --> 00:10:55.816
in milijon postane tisoč.

00:10:55.840 --> 00:10:58.096
Nastati mora kompleksno življenje -

00:10:58.120 --> 00:11:00.696
in tisoč postane ena.